        "item_apn4UL": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Landscape Design & Build",
            "content": "<p>We specialize in native habitat, natural resource enhancement, stormwater management, edible landscapes, and climate resilience. Collectively we have over a decade of experience creating habitat for residential, commercial, community, and public spaces. Browse our <a href=\"https://www.bloomsdaynatives.com/projects\">portfolio </a>to see some of the work we do.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_JWFgDY": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Installation",
            "content": "<p>We install resilient landscape projects designed to support habitat and community. Beyond habitat and native plants, we also install gathering areas, patios, pathways, raised beds, structures, fences, rain gardens, small retaining walls, living garden walls, and much more. See our <a href=\"https://www.bloomsdaynatives.com/projects\">portfolio </a>for some ideas, or reach out with your idea.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_XYJAwc": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Plant Orders & Contract Growing",
            "content": "<p>Have a project in the works that you need plants for? We offer contract growing services as well as plant ordering. See Nursery page for details and our Shop page to shop our inventory.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_jD3dYn": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ecological Consulting",
            "content": "<p>We oversee and help clients work through longer-term projects, providing a framework and tailored guidance at various project stages and scales. See our Ecological Consulting page for details.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
