        "column_pnKBaP": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2929sepowell.webp",
            "icon": "🌿",
            "heading": "Approach with Curiosity",
            "text": "<p>We begin every project with a fresh perspective and a desire to understand the story of your land and your unique goals. This typically starts with an on-site consultation, where you introduce us to the space and share your vision.</p><p>We ground our work in observation, listening closely to both the land and to you. By maintaining a sense of curiosity and wonder throughout the process, we uncover opportunities that are rooted in place and guided by purpose.</p>",
            "btn_label": "",
            "btn_url": ""
          }
        },
        "column_DDeNDF": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_9079.webp",
            "icon": "🌱",
            "heading": "Collaboration is Central",
            "text": "<p>As we move forward, we reflect on our observations and your goals to ensure we are aligned. Our team brings diverse perspectives and thoughtful alternatives to each project, enriching the design process through shared insight and experience.</p><p>We have experience facilitating and participating in community consultation and community-led design and planning processes. Open dialogue, feedback, and discussion are welcomed and encouraged throughout. Collaboration is not just a step in our process. It is the foundation of it.</p>",
            "btn_label": "",
            "btn_url": ""
          }
        },
        "column_8TwTNh": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_3751.webp",
            "icon": "🌸",
            "heading": "Plans are Dynamic",
            "text": "<p>Nature is never static, and neither are the ecosystems we are a part of. We design with the understanding that landscapes shift and evolve over time. Our approach is adaptive, like water; flexible and responsive in the face of changing conditions or unforeseen challenges.</p><p>We consider multiple outcomes and remain open in both mindset and communication throughout each phase of a project. Central to our work is preparing for the realities of a warming climate. We prioritize biodiversity and community care as foundational to building resilient, thriving habitats that endure and adapt over time.</p>",
            "btn_label": "",
            "btn_url": ""
          }
        }
